snippet.textDisplay:
if i ever got this I would make my favorite thing to make in Animal Crossing games. A jail. I just want to make Alcatraz. I want to see my villagers suffer. I want them to not realize they're permanently trapped in jail. I want them to give me their possessions because I said hi to them 3 times.

Yep, you can do that and I love it. My animal crossing pocket camp area is a jail too, even with cardboard bazookas and security disco drones. Once I can, I'm getting the cookie my drones are from and grab some fire pillars.

I get bored sometimes.
